Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上午8點 做便當
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是煎蛋 這是我的得意之作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了今天 我可是練習得都快厭煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要吃了這個 他的心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我睡過頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在這裏?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:46.23,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}くるくるまわる　君の瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:49.05,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}探してまわる　駅のホーム
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:54.14,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}響くファンファーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:57.34,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ガラガラ音をたてる街
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:01:00.25,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}とりあえず　耳を貸してみたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:06.71,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もうすぐ　消えるはずの世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.13,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:20.96,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もう二度と会えないような　そんな気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.33,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}運命が笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.69,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}臨界点を突破してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:31.49,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}限界ならすでに去って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:36.82,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}絶対的支配だって　崩壊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:42.71,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}終末理論は机上の　空論でしかないって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:53.27,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}0と1の世界線の果てから　叫ぶよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:02:01.89,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もうすぐ　君が会いに来るような気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:07.42,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕は目を閉じるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:56.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:46.23,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}轉啊轉 你的眼睛不停轉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:49.05,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在月台四處尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:54.14,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}號角聲在空中迴盪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:57.34,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}大街上轟轟作響
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:01:00.25,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}總之 先傾聽這聲音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:06.71,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在這個就要消逝的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.13,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:20.96,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}總是覺得 我們無法再度相會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.33,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}命運也在嘲笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.69,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}突破臨界點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:31.49,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}極限已然消去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:36.82,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}就算被絕對地支配 也讓它崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:42.71,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}末日理論無非是一紙空談
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:53.27,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在0與1的世界線的盡頭 呼喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:02:01.89,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}總是覺得 你即將來與我相會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:07.42,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那我 就閉上眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 今天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也馬上來介紹我們在城市裏發現的美食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特製出遊豪華便當 完成啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了 蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.11,0:02:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你要帶它到哪裏去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去約會吧 蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她拜託我教她做美味煎蛋卷的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不太會做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶能來幫忙 真是得救啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一點都不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會對象是多蕗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本不叫約會 而是跟蹤啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~ 做得不錯嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我們家的主婦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:02:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰是主婦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 荻野目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你要去哪觀察野鳥呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和田塚公園
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是巧啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶馬今天也有事要去那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 晶馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這是怎麼回…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 找準機會去搜那女人的包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找到「那個東西」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 老哥你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點瑣事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}現在臨時插入一則新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.88,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}從現場發回的報道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是女孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥你不用多久真的會被上天懲罰的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:40.13,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}嗯 現在我們就在現場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 荻目野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:42.53,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}今天早上 在和田塚的住宅街
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:47.61,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}有人說發現了幾天前市內研究所裏被盜的臭鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:53.34,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(945,72)}又臭又危險的"寵物"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:53.34,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1106,165)}有預謀的盜竊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕到現場的警察正在進行搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在附近的諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:57.34,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(654,567)}清君 一歲 （男）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果發現清君 請千萬不要捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先聯繫警察
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 這只臭鼬清君…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:04:01.31,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(926,67)}臭鼬出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你是去公園觀察野鳥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個也是…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運安排之類的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 你之前好像說過這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.46,slogan,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(159,378)}小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.46,slogan,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz327.639\pos(161,506)}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.46,slogan,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1055,289)}順手牽羊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天接下來要發生的事情…都是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很重要的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允許失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:49.77,flashback_br,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(300,0)}高倉家·晚上 起居室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.19,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}秘密交談的兄弟倆。蘋果和企鵝罐的關係是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.77,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}2號忍受著頭部的灼熱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過「命運已經記載好了」 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 是記錄在紙上的 書和筆記之類的東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那和我們追尋的企鵝罐又有什麼聯繫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 能解開謎團的鑰匙應該就在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以至今為止我們一直找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是因為那女人一直貼身不離地帶著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題就是要怎麼拿到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 是在那裏面?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:32.69,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\pos(1048,372)}那份「愛戀」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:32.69,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\pos(993,533)}能被允許嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:32.69,writings4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fay0.23\frz281.937\pos(1238,177)}命運之戀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運之戀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗王子 御~駕出行!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 我的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是值得我們紀念的重要日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 請不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同前去吧! 去往屬於我們的極樂園!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯! 請讓我追隨您吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我追隨您吧! 無論天涯海角!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上午十點 在噴泉廣場會合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟計劃一樣 完美!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我就在此告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…沒事 我幫你拿到會合地點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說為什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥啊! 好臭 好臭 好臭!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明接下來還有重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還有必須要做的事啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的好臭啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗要來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們換衣服!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣能瞞得過去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是多蕗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然與我無關 不過他那便服太土了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你男朋友也來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男…男朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人只是認識而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他聽說了今天的事 不管我怎麼勸他都說要來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是喜歡野鳥的朋友的話 我無論何時都很歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這不是高倉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高倉是我班上的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 原來你們認識啊 真巧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 是錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛剛開始就有股怪怪的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個人! 臭的是這個人!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人昨天掉進糞池裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今早還淋了半年沒洗過的烏龜水箱裏的水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了「你很臭別跟來」 但他根本沒聽進去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是跟你添了天大的麻煩 對不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來穿的襯衫還挺漂亮的 真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又是和一對可愛的情侶一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好 我給你們介紹個老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是時籠百合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:38.13,flashback_br,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(300,0)}多蕗的公寓 多蕗房間前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:36.12,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}直面殘酷的現實。真想忘掉。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:38.13,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}對了，這女人那時也在房間裏。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要來點咖喱?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上她是個演員哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在SunShiny歌劇團扮演少女角色…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下 您是時籠百合小姐嗎? 隸屬虹組的那位?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:08:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能見到您實在太榮幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在下次演出中扮演的瑪麗 超讓人期待的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮演瑪麗的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:26.33,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就如那女演員之星下凡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:35.39,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛若舞台中央 盛放的那朵玫瑰花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:39.81,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 眾人皆投目光於我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:43.40,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆因我而沉醉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:46.94,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fabulous Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等會! 這情節發展是怎麼回事!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的幻想?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來 停下來啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:58.39,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我心獨鍾情一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:02.19,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並全部奉獻給他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:09.04,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是那迷人的鳥之王子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:10.84,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是演員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.68,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是演員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.56,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是演員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:17.27,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是演員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:29.03,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}請跟我握個手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡和一份「大吃一驚巧克力聖代」是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.58,writings6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(449,323)\frz4.455}我知道你尋找的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.58,writings6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz4.455\pos(569,547)}如果想知道詳情的話，今天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.58,writings6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz4.455\pos(568,599)}11點到下圖所示的家庭餐廳來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰知道我們的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他想得到企鵝罐的人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 被算計了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們組成了「高倉冠葉戀愛受害者協會」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是久寶小姐號召的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿佐美她?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把被你欺騙的可憐女孩們召集起來 然後進行抗議
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你玩弄純情少女心的這份責任…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要讓你好好地承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天罰啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又飛走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 肯定是這個臭臭的人不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天就來悠閒地散個步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近只顧練習新劇目 已經很久沒這麼自在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你邀請我過來 多蕗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦 我也沒做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會輸給你 我可是帶了特製豪華出遊便當的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 也差不多該吃午飯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊啊啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的便當…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 我?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因為你太臭了 所以把便當放在那邊」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你自己說的嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎麼補償我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下計劃就泡湯了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是必須在12點半吃午飯的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 我覺得完全不用擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害! 這些全是百合小姐做的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只是早上用冰箱裏剩下的材料做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定怎麼都比不上蘋果的便當啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正裝的都是從商店地下食品區買來的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這個好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來吃一塊嘗嘗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:24.01,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果沒有麵包 讓他們吃蛋糕不就好了?」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:24.01,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}註：相傳為法國大革命中被處死的瑪麗·安托瓦內特皇后所說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:29.05,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go take a fabulous lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:34.32,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 請享用我親手做的佳餚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~竟如此絕贊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:36.65,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(733,664)}tres bien
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是SunShiny Miracle !
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:42.74,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thus such a beautiful lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:46.17,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 章魚香腸如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:50.06,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜點也準備好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「12點半 和多蕗吃便當」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「他高興地說很好吃」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 和計劃的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運還是站在我這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午3點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要完成這個任務 就等於是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟王子殿下的親吻…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:27.48,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將要告訴你 這秘密的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:34.45,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運啊 就記載在這
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「下午3點 他抱緊我 呼吸拂過我的脖子」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳不已呀~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 蘋果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個計劃告訴我嘛告訴我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼想知道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 想知道想知道~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密就是這個!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好像很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:58.55,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕毛毛蟲的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:02.15,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子殿下拯救了她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.18,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕觸碰的肩膀與手兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:06.02,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互凝視的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:06.81,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:11.99,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 兩個人墜入愛河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:15.28,song,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 今天凡爾賽宮人真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:21.25,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}註：年輕的瑪麗對杜巴利夫人說的唯一一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 恐怖的毒毛蟲掉到了我的肩膀上!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 請您 勇氣過人的王子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我這可憐的女子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要去救她!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 王子殿下! 快來這邊吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子 糟糕了 王妃殿下她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 毛毛蟲!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種庶民就別管了 趕緊來這邊啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…? 等會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我們一起去藥店 買支叮咬靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:04.91,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}長滿毛的傢伙 應該是革命政府的奸細吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我說…等等啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:06.32,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}看我不把你煮了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要「抱緊我」「在脖子上吹氣」啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 之前的咖喱 多謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得一般般啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗也誇過了哦 說「百合做的料理真不錯呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你的鞋子我也好好處理掉了 你放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事就當做我們兩人之間的秘密好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你是沒有勝算的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧? 疼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 只是有點刺痛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 還有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「10點見面」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「12點半吃便當」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「3點被呼吸拂過心跳不已」?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的計劃?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「4點在池塘邊第一次…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「親吻」?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不只剩15分鐘了麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:24.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那我們去找栗耳短腳鵯好不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:25.89,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哇 好想去見一下~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本連丁點的氣氛都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會搞定的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對 4點鐘要跟多蕗接吻!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我! 救救我!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果公主!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,.oO.oO.oO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 何等悲慘的事啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了打破邪惡魔女的魔法 就只能這樣了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛拯救世界!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊蘋果 拿出勇氣來!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為童話故事裏能贏得白馬王子的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是不畏險阻 勇敢的公主啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栗耳短腳鵯啊 從小養大的話就會跟人很親近…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:35.63,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}栗耳短腳鵯：日本國內常見的野鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日記?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說她的命運已經記載在這上面了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的假的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救救我!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要這樣…死掉了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能與多蕗親吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊媽媽 我沒能遵守好命運
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道爸爸現在怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後還是想再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見見他啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你掉進池子裏溺水了 剛才我都不知道該怎麼辦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然馬上就做人工呼吸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人工呼吸?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個姐姐剛才跟哥哥親過了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小健不要亂說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…和多蕗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和多蕗吻過啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 為什麼我要遭這罪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大顯身手了呢 救人英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳進池子 還做了人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很帥氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都干了啥啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:51.03,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fad(2000,0)}晚上9點 赤阪見附站\N升降機（Elevator） 穿紅鞋的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但是那樣做好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺反而被當做個很麻煩的女人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭 得趕緊碾碎掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 這也是計劃的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一手已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 「下一手」到底是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上9點 赤阪見附車站
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動扶梯 穿著紅鞋的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:44.41,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,666)}Escalator
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:54.96,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}4{\fs30\pos(640,630)}TH STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:54.96,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄落的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:16.35,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}全てがもし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:20.02,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}決められてたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:29.04,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕らはどうして　もがくのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:33.20,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}それは、君じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:36.90,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}君の、せいじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:44.39,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}悲しみはもうたくさんなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:48.24,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}だから、そうじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.39,0:22:52.17,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}今の、ままじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:59.84,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}うまく伝えきれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:07.25,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR MY FUTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.50,0:23:16.19,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR YOUR FUTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:16.35,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}如果這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:20.02,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}早已命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:29.04,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那我們又為何 仍在苦苦掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:33.20,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}其實那 與你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:36.90,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}你並沒有 做錯什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:44.39,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}悲傷已經足夠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:48.24,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}因此 並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.39,0:22:52.17,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}並不是 現在這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:59.84,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}只是無法將心情傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:07.25,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR MY FUTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.50,0:23:16.19,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR YOUR FUTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話 那本筆記能借給我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一小會就行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用完了馬上就還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.67,0:23:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存戰略 叮咬靈

